projectShare.description1: When you share this project, we'll take a snapshot of its configuration that includes instructions, connectors, knowledge files, and task definitions. You can share the generated link with others and they can use it to launch their own instance of the project from your snapshot.
projectShare.description2: If you make changes to your project, you can return to this page to take a new snapshot. When you do, owners of existing projects launched using your link will be notified that an update is available and new instances will automatically get the new version.
